This creates a comprehensive advanced settings page with:
Performance Controls:
OCR concurrency threading (1-8 threads)
Image cache size limits with auto-cleanup
GPU acceleration toggle for WebGL/TensorFlow.js
Lazy loading distance thresholds
Memory pressure handling
Security Hardening:
Runtime integrity verification
WASM sandboxing with CSP
Hardware-backed encryption for API keys
Network isolation enforcement
Security audit logging
OCR Engine Tuning:
Tesseract page segmentation modes (including manga-optimized)
Neural net vs legacy engine selection
Vertical text (tategaki) optimization
Experimental handwriting detection
Experimental Features:
On-device LLM translation (WebGPU)
Predictive preloading via behavioral analysis
Cross-bubble translation context
Desktop overlay mode
Developer debug mode with performance overlay
System Information Panel:
Real-time hardware capability detection (WebGPU, memory, cores)
Storage quota monitoring
Cache statistics with manual clearing
Diagnostic log export
One-click reset to defaults
The component includes debounced setting persistence, immediate runtime communication for critical toggles, and comprehensive warning labels for potentially destabilizing options.